token_info.name: Feast of the Black Nazarene x Holga
token_info.description: Photos taken using Holga + Kodak Professional T-Max 100. The Feast of the Black Nazarene, held every January 9, is the biggest religious event in the Philippines characterized by a day-long procession that attracts millions of devotees. Artist: Marlon Hacla (@sintang_ligalig). HTML slideshow. Creation Date: April 19, 2021.
